  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/12ca638a86b599a3665458a96a8642de.avif?t=1746799203\" width=600 height=140 /></span><br>Brace for intense survival gameplay as you face relentless waves of enemies and epic boss encounters. Strategize your approach, adapt to dynamic challenges, and earn upgrades to evolve into an unstoppable force. This singular environment serves as the backdrop for an immersive and gripping journey where every decision can mean the difference between survival and defeat.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c5b74454073cbfaca16177fc8f789201.poster.avif?t=1746799203\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c5b74454073cbfaca16177fc8f789201.webm?t=1746799203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c5b74454073cbfaca16177fc8f789201.mp4?t=1746799203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br>Survival Intensity: Engage in an unforgiving battle for survival against hordes of enemies and challenging bosses.<br>Original Soundtrack: Immerse yourself in the atmospheric world with a captivating and dynamic musical score.<br>Upgrade System: Customize your character's abilities, weaponry, and defenses to adapt to evolving threats.<br>Singular Environment: Explore a richly detailed and evolving cityscape, each area presenting unique challenges.<br>Unravel the Unknown: Piece together the narrative as you confront your past and the enigmatic forces that control the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c482a5824bd74552439638964e5ab6ff.poster.avif?t=1746799203\" width=600 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c482a5824bd74552439638964e5ab6ff.webm?t=1746799203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775060/extras/c482a5824bd74552439638964e5ab6ff.mp4?t=1746799203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
